OL,3,CReform Senedd Member facing 14-day ban
OL,4,Cover racial slur made in a WhatsApp
OL,5,Cgroup
OL,7,FReform's only Senedd Member faces a
OL,8,Ftwo-week suspension over a racial slur
OL,9,Fshe used in a WhatsApp message.
OL,11,FLaura Anne Jones, who defected from
OL,12,Fthe Welsh Conservatives to Reform UK
OL,13,Fin July 2025, used a racial slur to
OL,14,Fdescribe Chinese people in August
OL,15,F2023. She later apologised.
OL,17,FThe Senedd's standards committee has
OL,18,Fnow recommended she be suspended from
OL,19,Fthe Senedd's debating chamber for two
OL,20,Fweeks.
