OL,7,FMSs will have to approve the
OL,8,Fsuspension next week for it to come
OL,9,Finto force.
OL,11,FMs Jones used a slur about Chinese
OL,12,Fpeople in a WhatsApp group, during a
OL,13,Fdiscussion of the Chinese-owned app
OL,14,FTikTok in August 2023.
OL,16,FShe has previously apologised for the
OL,17,Fremark but the Senedd standards
OL,18,Fcommittee said her conduct "fell far
OL,19,Fbelow the standards expected" of an MS.
