OL,7,FIn its report, members of the
OL,8,Fcommittee said: "The committee is
OL,9,Fclear that inappropriate and offensive
OL,10,Fcomments have no place in our Senedd,
OL,11,For society more widely. These messages
OL,12,Fwere contained within an office group
OL,13,FWhatsApp chat, rather than a public
OL,14,Fforum. However the code is clear that
OL,15,Fit applies to Members at all times."
