OL,7,FThe standards committee made its
OL,8,Frecommendation following an
OL,9,Finvestigation by Senedd standards
OL,10,Fcommissioner Douglas Bain, who was
OL,11,Ftasked with considering three sets of
OL,12,Fallegations against the MS, including
OL,13,Fa complaint she had made a racist
OL,14,Fcomment and had failed to address
OL,15,Fdiscriminatory behaviour.
