OL,7,FMr Bain found that in a WhatsApp
OL,8,Fexchange with a staff member in August
OL,9,F2023, Ms Jones referred to a former
OL,10,Fstaff member as "a bitter, twisted,
OL,11,Fuseless person" and posted "I tried to
OL,12,Fbe so understanding. I even asked if
OL,13,F(they) had ADHD or something and if
OL,14,F(they) needed extra support ... cos
OL,15,Fsomething isn't right with (them)!?"
OL,17,FMr Bain found that Ms Jones regretted
OL,18,Fthat these comments had become public.
