OL,7,FThe committee also ruled Ms Jones had
OL,8,Fbreached the code of conduct by
OL,9,Ffailing to challenge offensive
OL,10,Fcomments made by a member of staff in
OL,11,FNovember 2023.
OL,13,FDuring a WhatsApp exchange with Ms
OL,14,FJones, the employee said: "And Suella
OL,15,F(Braverman, former Conservative home
OL,16,Fsecretary) was correct in what she
OL,17,Fsaid too. We have two tier policing.
OL,18,FIt was clear over the weekend if your
OL,19,F(sic) white working class you get
OL,20,Fhammered, if you're an Islamist it's
OL,21,Fall fine, spew all the hate you want."
