OL,7,FMs Jones did not reprimand the member
OL,8,Fof staff at the time but has since
OL,9,Fdescribed the comments as being
OL,10,Funacceptable.
OL,12,FIn November 2023, Ms Jones did not
OL,13,Freprimand a member of staff for
OL,14,Fposting during a WhatsApp exchange:
OL,15,F"And Suella was correct in what she
OL,16,Fsaid too. We have two tier policing.
OL,17,FIt was clear over the weekend if your
OL,18,Fwhite working class you get hammered,
OL,19,Fif you're an Islamist it's all fine,
OL,20,Fspew all the hate you want."
