OL,8,Faccepted that the post was
OL,9,Funacceptable.
OL,11,FThe committee said: "It points to an
OL,12,Foffice culture where there was little
OL,13,Frespect towards others or any
OL,14,Fconsideration of what may be found
OL,15,Foffensive."
OL,17,FThe MS has apologised again for the
OL,18,F"regrettable" comments made in a
OL,19,Fprivate message.
