OL,7,FShe said she was "delighted to have
OL,8,Ffinally been cleared of any wrongdoing
OL,9,Fin relation to the malicious
OL,10,Faccusation of fraudulent activity" and
OL,11,Fwas looking forward to "drawing a line
OL,12,Funder this after nearly two years of
OL,13,Fbeing hounded over it, and the
OL,14,Fdetrimental impact that it has on both
OL,15,Fme and my young family".
OL,17,FThe MS added: "I would like to thank
OL,18,Fboth the police and Standards
OL,19,FCommissioner for their thorough
OL,20,Finvestigation, and I accept their
OL,21,Fconclusions."
