OL,7,FA Reform UK Wales spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Laura has rightly apologised for her
OL,9,Fcomments, made in a private WhatsApp,
OL,10,Fand has made a clear effort to make
OL,11,Famends for these comments. However, it
OL,12,Fis quite clear that there is a serious
OL,13,Fissue with two-tier policing in this
OL,14,Fcountry, and no politician should be
OL,15,Fbarred from our national parliament
